articles.description: Trae Young's spirits were buoyed by a surprise phone call Wednesday from Hall of Famer Oscar Robertson, who gave the Sooners freshman "some good advice."
articles.headline: Trae Young gets 'some good advice' from Hall of Famer Oscar Robertson

videos.description: Marek Dolezaj swats away a shot for the Orange.
videos.headline: Syracuse's Dolezaj gets a clean block

videos.description: LaDarien Griffin catches a quick pass from Courtney Stockard, and flushes home a two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: St. Bonaventure's Griffith slams it down

videos.description: Great ball movement leads to a wide open Jaylen Adams, who buries a 3-pointer for the Bonnies.
videos.headline: St. Bonaventure's Adams swishes a 3-pointer

videos.description: Jaylen Adams' 3-pointer bounces off the rim and the glass before falling to cap a 7-0 run for the Bonnies.
videos.headline: The iron kind to Adams

videos.description: Frank Howard drive the lane and hammers home a right-handed slam for the Orange.
videos.headline: Syracuse's Howard throws down thunder dunk

videos.description: Jaylen Adams hits his third 3-pointer of the first half for the Bonnies.
videos.headline: Adams stays hot from downtown with 3s

videos.description: Off the steal, Matt Mobley leads the fast break and finishes with a 17ft jumper for the Bonnies.
videos.headline: St. Bonaventure's Mobley buries jumper in transition

videos.description: Matt Mobley's second 3-pointer of the second half pushes the Bonnies to a 7-0 run.
videos.headline: Mobley's nasty crossover leads to 3-pointer

videos.description: LaDarien Griffith hammers home slam dunk off the lob feed from Jaylen Adams to cap a 9-0 run for the Bonnies.
videos.headline: Adams, Griffith connect for alley-oop slam

videos.description: After a miss shot Tyus Battle blocks the shot of  LaDarien Griffith, but the Bonnies keep possession.
videos.headline: End-to-end action leads to Battle block for Syracuse

videos.description: Amadi Ikpeze receives the pass from Jaylen Adams who flushes home the dunk and is fouled for the Bonnies.
videos.headline: St. Bonaventure's Ikpeze muscles up for dunk

videos.description: Paschal Chukwu gets to the rim for a layup and is fouled. Chukwu hits the free throw to tie the game in the second half.
videos.headline: Syracuse's Chukwu ties the game with and-1 layup
